LongGammaWrapperClaimResidual
├── when claimResidual is called after the position is Closed
│   ├── it reconciles surviving collateral and sets the claimed flag before any redeem
│   ├── it computes per token residual as max of surviving minus cost and zero
│   ├── it redeems the cap aware minimum of residual shares and maxRedeem to the stored user
│   ├── it pays a figure derived from surviving collateral and not from the upfront deposit
│   └── it emits ResidualClaimed
├── when claimResidual is called while the position is still Open
│   └── it reverts WrongState because numberOfLegs is not zero
└── when claimResidual is called a second time
    └── it reverts AlreadyClaimed
